OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBright or sunny spells and
OL,6,Fshowers, the best sunnier periods
OL,7,Fexpected during the morning. The
OL,8,Fshowers could be heavy, perhaps the
OL,9,Fodd rumble of thunder. Moderate
OL,10,Fwesterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FPartly cloudy this evening
OL,13,Fwith showers, some heavy and thundery
OL,14,Fat first. Most showers will die out in
OL,15,Fthe early hours, the best of the
OL,16,Fclearer spells for Argyll.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
