OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA mainly dry and partly cloudy
OL,6,Fmorning. Sunny spells will develop
OL,7,Fduring the day alongside a few
OL,8,Fshowers, some of which may be on the
OL,9,Fheavy side.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FRain
OL,12,For showers on Tuesday and Wednesday,
OL,13,Foccasionally heavy. Drier on Thursday.
OL,14,FMilder than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
